  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `ChatSession.cs` + `ChatSessionFile.cs`. Identify the current shape of `UploadedFiles[]` items.</step>
    <step order="2">Grep for R6 task 051 SaveTabsAsync precedent (likely in `SessionPersistenceService.cs` + `StoredSession.cs`).</step>
    <step order="3">Add the 8 enriched fields to `ChatSessionFile` (or equivalent):
      - `SummaryText` (string?, nullable)
      - `ClassifiedDocType` (string?, nullable)
      - `ClassifiedConfidence` (double?, nullable)
      - `Sections` (List&lt;SectionInfo&gt;, default empty)
      - `TableMetadata` (List&lt;TableInfo&gt;, default empty)
      - `Citations` (List&lt;CitationReference&gt;, default empty)
      - `PageCount` (int?, nullable)
      - `Language` (string?, nullable, default "en")

      Use `[JsonPropertyName]` if other peer fields use it; otherwise rely on default casing.</step>
    <step order="4">Author unit test: serialize an existing-shape `ChatSession` JSON (no enriched fields) and verify deserialization produces field defaults; serialize a new-shape `ChatSession` and verify roundtrip.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `dotnet build`.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet test` for serialization test.</step>
    <step order="7">Measure BFF publish size.</step>
    <step order="8">code-review + adr-check.</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md: 071 ŌåÆ Ō£ģ.</step>
  </steps>

